Invocation Name: trending on github
des: The open-source world is exciting, active, and constantly changing. Use this skill to find out what project is trending on GitHub for the day. You can choose to learn about a project for a particular programming language or the top project for all languages.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
